eason}\\n\"\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3540:    if not claimed_issue_worktree_is_valid(claimed_issue, \"human-intervention analysis\"):\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3557:            f\"ERROR: Human-intervention analysis failed for issue #{claimed_issue.issue['number']}: {exc!r}\",\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3712:        f\"ai/{authenticated_login}/human-intervention/\"\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3855:    \"\"\"Refresh library logs on an already pushed human-intervention branch.\"\"\"\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3912:    \"\"\"Post the human-intervention comment and always attempt to apply the label.\"\"\"\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3921:                f\"ERROR: Failed to post human-intervention comment to issue #{issue_number}: {exc!r}\",\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3942:    \"\"\"Post a human-intervention comment and label when an issue run needs follow-up.\"\"\"\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3960:            f\"ERROR: Failed to apply human-intervention follow-up to issue #{claimed_issue.issue['number']}: {exc!r}\",\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:2:name: close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:3:description: Close batches of graalvm-reachability-metadata pull requests that either have the `human-intervention` label or failing CI, and revert their linked issues by clearing assignees and moving project status to `Todo`.\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:6:# Close Human-Intervention and Failing-CI PRs\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:18:- The PR has the `human-intervention` label.\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:29:   - Fetch open human-intervention PRs:\n./skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:31:     gh pr list -R oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata --state open --label human-intervention --limit 200 --json number,title,url,labels,statusCheckRollup\n./skills/close